{"tid":1287242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[第四宗反送中自殺個案]　死者親友冀政府回應訴求　「真正能阻止年輕人絕望係政府」","createTime":"2019-07-05T06:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:41:40.000Z","uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40d01248244beccfed4a355e23e9f55ca1fb85fe","tid":1287242,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"第四宗反送中自殺個案　死者親友冀政府回應訴求　「真正能阻止年輕人絕望係政府」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%AE%97%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E8%83%BD%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E4%BF%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=258099a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%2F&h=d3e3a04d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%AE%97%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E8%83%BD%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E4%BF%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/</a><br />\n<br />\n這是第四宗涉及反對《逃犯條例》修訂的自殺個案。7 月 3 日清晨，<span style=\"color: red;\">28 歲的麥小姐在長沙灣住所墮樓身亡，網上流傳有關她留在房間的遺物和遺書，表明她反對《逃犯條例》修訂及爭取民主的意向。</span>她的朋友獲家屬同意，主動聯絡《立場新聞》證實她的死訊，並希望通過傳媒傳達麥小姐的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n死者的朋友向《立場》表示，當日下午收到通知，趕往她的住所，在她的房間發現她留下的字句，她又在床上擺放了一張矮桌，上面放有兩張紙，寫有「不是民選的政府是不會回應訴求」、「甚麼也改變不了的無力感令人煎熬」等字句，並放了眼罩、生理鹽水、相機等物品，以及留給家人和朋友的信。朋友和家人商量後，同意讓外界得悉她希望傳達的訊息，「覺得佢想將遺願話俾人聽」。<br />\n<br />\n朋友形容她是樂觀積極的人，「好多人會覺得佢係一個開心果」，近日一直關注《逃犯條例》爭議，但事前並不認為她有情緒困擾或其他個人問題，「事前唔會 sense 到」。"},{"pid":"d62f74052e60a21d89843721f2823a46561706c4","tid":1287242,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"香港既未來會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7a2f2e16394837f884ab902f690538d6a0e1ad","tid":1287242,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"仲有一句<br />\n「香港需要的是革命」"},{"pid":"a2ba8e59aa1c36a3daff42428ac0ffb52f78d6d5","tid":1287242,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1535766/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3%E5%94%90%E6%A8%93%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1535766%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%2594%2590%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A2%25AE